name: KK Concrete
overview:
Established in the year 2012, at Pune (Maharashtra, India), we, “K. K. Concrete”, are the eminent organization involved in manufacturing and supplying a wide gamut of Concrete Furniture, Manhole Covers And Frames, Railway Platform Coping, Grass Paving, Floor Slabs, Tactiles, Interlocking Pavers, Boundary Wall and Bollards etc.

Our Products : Concrete Furniture, Manhole Covers And Frames, Railway Platform Coping, Grass Paving, Floor Slabs, Tactiles, Interlocking Pavers, Boundary Wall and Bollards etc.

Our Clients: Being a client-centric firm, our main motto is to attain maximum clients’ satisfaction by offering them the best quality products. Also, we offer our clients customized products which are fabricated in compliance with the set international quality standards.

Our Certificate: ISO, CE, FDA, OHSAS etc.

Infrastructure: We have a state-of-the-art infrastructure facility that is well-equipped with advanced machines and contemporary technology that assist us to manufacture the best quality products.

Our Quality: We ensure that offered range is manufactured by us in compliance with the set international quality standards. Manufactured using high grade basic material, these are extensively appreciated for their consistent quality.
